<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:12:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特斯拉12月中国产电动汽车销量同比增长68.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-jump-687-yy-december-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周三的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉12月份销售了94,139辆中国制造的电动汽车(EV)，同比增长68.7%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 09:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-jump-687-yy-december-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉12月中国产电动汽车销量同比增长68.7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-687-yy-december-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周三的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉12月份销售了94,139辆中国制造的电动汽车，同比增长68.7%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 08:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-grow-687-yy-december-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利12月外资加速抛售中国股市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-funds-accelerated-china-equity-sell-off-december-morgan-stanley-2024-01-03/</link><description>摩根士丹利分析师表示，全球多头基金在 12 月以 2023 年最快的速度抛售中国股票，因为它们急于满足赎回要求并实现多元化，远离世界第二大经济体。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 08:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/foreign-funds-accelerated-china-equity-sell-off-december-morgan-stanley-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中方表示愿向日本抗震救灾提供帮助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-is-willing-provide-help-japan-earthquake-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中方愿就元旦发生的特大地震向日方提供必要帮助。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 07:49:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-it-is-willing-provide-help-japan-earthquake-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国顶级银行收紧对规模较小银行的风险敞口以遏制信贷风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-tighten-exposure-smaller-peers-curb-credit-risk-sources-say-2024-01-03/</link><description>三名消息人士称，中国一些顶级银行加强了对规模较小银行资产质量的审查，并收紧了银行间拆借标准，以在不断加深的房地产债务危机波及整个经济之际遏制信贷风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 07:45:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-top-banks-tighten-exposure-smaller-peers-curb-credit-risk-sources-say-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国基金经理急于创建追踪新A50指数的基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-money-managers-rush-create-funds-tracking-new-a50-index-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国的基金管理公司正忙于创建追踪新推出的沪深 A50 指数的基金，分析师表示，该指数比中国的股票基准更好地反映了中国的经济形势和政府的优先事项。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-money-managers-rush-create-funds-tracking-new-a50-index-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>大选后中国可能对台湾采取“鹰派”军事压制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hawkish-china-military-squeeze-taiwan-likely-after-election-2024-01-03/</link><description>无论谁赢得台湾备受关注的选举，台湾海峡的军备竞赛以及中国对北京声称其“神圣”领土的岛屿的军事压力都不太可能结束。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hawkish-china-military-squeeze-taiwan-likely-after-election-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>海外人士反驳香港对黎智英进行安全审判的指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/overseas-figures-refute-allegations-hong-kong-security-trial-jimmy-lai-2024-01-03/</link><description>在香港民主人士黎智英的国家安全审判中被点名的几名海外活动人士、右翼活动人士和政界人士驳斥了一名政府检察官在法庭上提出的关于他们与黎智英勾结的指控。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 06:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/overseas-figures-refute-allegations-hong-kong-security-trial-jimmy-lai-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪将向经销商发放20亿元奖励以助其完成销售目标--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-give-dealers-2-bln-yuan-hitting-sales-target-sources-2024-01-03/</link><description>据两位知情经销商透露，第四季度全球电动汽车销量首次超过特斯拉的比亚迪将向其中国经销商发放总计数十亿元人民币的奖励。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 05:11:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-give-dealers-2-bln-yuan-hitting-sales-target-sources-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国公布下一代航母的新图片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-new-images-its-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-01-03/</link><description>中国官方媒体公布了中国迄今为止最先进航母的新图片，其中包括可以从甲板上弹射更多类型飞机的下一代发射轨道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 04:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-unveils-new-images-its-next-generation-aircraft-carrier-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国官员敦促台湾人民在选举中做出“正确选择”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-official-urges-taiwans-people-make-correct-choice-election-2024-01-03/</link><description>周三，一名中国高级官员敦促台湾人民在台湾即将举行的选举中做出“正确选择”，他称这次选举关系到和平与战争、繁荣与衰落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 02:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-official-urges-taiwans-people-make-correct-choice-election-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在主要空军基地附近的岛屿上空发现中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-three-chinese-balloons-flew-across-island-2024-01-03/</link><description>台湾国防部表示，三个中国气球飞越台湾并靠近一个空军基地。在 1 月 13 日选举之前，台湾对中国的军事和政治活动保持高度警惕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jan 2024 01:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-three-chinese-balloons-flew-across-island-2024-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>巴克莱因需求担忧而降级后，苹果跌至七周低点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</link><description>由于担心 2024 年从 iPhone 到 Mac 等苹果设备的需求仍将疲软，巴克莱银行下调了这家全球市值最高公司的股价评级，周二苹果股价下跌近 3.6%，至七周低点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-starts-2024-with-barclays-downgrade-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国打破高温记录，酷热天气从北到南烘烤城市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</link><description>2023年，中国的炎热天气有所缓解，从北京到上海的气温记录都被打破，这与同样席卷世界大部分地区的全球热浪现象相呼应，引发了人们对全球气候变化的更多担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 14:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/china-breaks-heat-records-2023-sweltering-weather-baked-cities-north-south-2024-01-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉第四季度汽车交付量创历史新高，但中国比亚迪抢夺电动汽车头把交椅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-fourth-quarter-deliveries-beat-estimates-2024-01-02/</link><description>特斯拉在第四季度交付了创纪录的电动汽车数量，超出了市场预期，并实现了 2023 年的目标，但由于销量输给了中国比亚迪，失去了最大电动汽车制造商的地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jan 2024 13:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-fourth-quarter-deliveries-beat-estimates-2024-01-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>